Scientific Officer on probation at the establishment of the Directorate of Judicial Assistant Scientific Laboratory, Group-B cadre in the Direct Service Quota Vacancies Candidates recommended by the Maharashtra Public Service Commission are referred to the Reference No. The appointment has been made for a probationary period of 2 years as per the Government Decision herein. The proposal to terminate the probationary period of the said officer was made by the Director, Directorate of Judicial Assistant Scientific Laboratories, Maharashtra State, Mumbai vide Reference No. 2 The letter here has been submitted to the government. Accordingly, in the following table, Column No. As the officers in (2) have satisfactorily completed their probationary period in the rank of Scientific Officer, Group-B, their probationary period in this post is being terminated on the date mentioned in column (5) before their name in column No. (6) It is hereby approved to continue his appointment with regular supervision from the date in question.
